rticle titled \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736156-palantir-take-profits-before-its-too-late\"><em>Palantir: Take Profits Before It's Too Late</em></a>\" where I initiated a \"<em>Sell</em>\" rating for the stock. My primary argument was that Palantir's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150167239/image_2150167239.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747517-palantir-losing-momentum-2025-could-mark-significant-downturn", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 21:04:27", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747509", "title": "A Dividend Anchor In A Sea Of Volatility: Genco Shipping's Steadfast Strategy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of the metal mineral port\" data-id=\"2187994787\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">wen ya/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Investment Thesis:</strong></p> <p>Genco Shipping &amp; Trading (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GNK\" title=\"Genco Shipping &amp; Trading Limited\">GNK</a></span>) stands out due to its strong capital structure which cushions the company\u2019s financials from the heaving cyclicality of deep-sea dry bulk shipping. The company\u2019s management has over the past few years successfully executed</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2187994787/image_2187994787.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747509-dividend-anchor-in-a-sea-of-volatility-genco-shipping-steadfast-strategy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:50:34", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747505", "title": "QQQ: Why Another 83% Tech Crash Should Not Be Ruled Out", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman\" data-id=\"155351397\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">D-Keine</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In my last <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4664387-qqq-managing-bubble-risks\">article</a> on the Invesco QQQ Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QQQ\" title=\"Invesco QQQ Trust ETF\">QQQ</a></span>) in January, I warned of a parabolic rise in tech stocks before the bubble eventually bursts. After rising a further 25%, the risks are now overwhelmingly tilted to the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155351397/image_155351397.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747505-qqq-why-another-83-percent-tech-crash-should-not-be-ruled-out", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:36:52", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747504", "title": "Stocks May Melt-Up Like It's 1999", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cityscape thailand with investment theme background and stock market chart\" data-id=\"1031993036\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3092px\" height=\"1739px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">primeimages</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The U.S. equity market has delivered two years of enormous returns, with the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) up 24.2% and 23.3% in 2023 and 2024, respectively. Now, looking at the performance in 2025, investors may be worried that similar returns may not be sustainable. Indeed, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1031993036/image_1031993036.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747504-stocks-may-melt-up-like-its-1999", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:30:17", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747503", "title": "Major Signals Point To Market Top: Investment Risk Mitigation Is Prudent Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Price crash and bear market\" data-id=\"1079127056\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5354px\" height=\"3569px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">24K-Production</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Several valuation and behavioral indicators are signaling that a generational stock market top is forming. While periods of overvaluation can persist, we advise reducing equity exposure in the <a href=\"https://www.barrons.com/livecoverage/stock-market-today-122724/card/the-magnificent-seven-stocks-are-selling-off-qlZz7WDyJL9MCBZskXUs\" rel=\"nofollow\">Magnificent Seven</a>, capitalization weighted indices like the S&amp;P 500 (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1079127056/image_1079127056.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747503-major-signals-point-to-market-top-investment-risk-mitigation-is-prudent-now", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:25:12", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747502", "title": "Silence Therapeutics: Simply No Match For Its Orally Dosed Rival (Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A single professional athlete covers her face in disappointment while sitting on the bench.\" data-id=\"1475830028\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Lighthouse Films/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Silence Therapeutics plc</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SLN\" title=\"Silence Therapeutics plc\">SLN</a></span>) dropped nearly 75% overnight on November 18 after presenting data from lead candidate Zerlasiran, a small-interfering RNA targeting Lipoprotein(a) reduction in patients. Looking through the data, I couldn\u2019t find the problem right away. Here</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1475830028/image_1475830028.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747502-silence-therapeutics-simply-no-match-for-its-orally-dosed-rival-downgrade", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 20:18:36", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747501", "title": "Verastem: Planning The PDUFA Run-Up", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Caucasian woman running up staircase\" data-id=\"543195141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/543195141/image_543195141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/54319